  "title": "Clinic Assistant",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Responsibilities / Duties:</strong></u></p>\n<p>• Patient registration</p>\n<p>• Preparation of Cases for Health screening, reviews</p>\n<p>• Attending to Patient enquiries</p>\n<p>• Billing</p>\n<p>• Dispense medications</p>\n<p>• Submission of Medisave, CHAS claims</p>\n<p>• Medical records scanning</p>\n<p>• Triage</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p>\n<p>• Minimum GCE 'N' or 'O' Level</p>\n<p>• Prior min. 2 years experience in admin support, customer service or healthcare</p>\n<p>preferred</p>\n<p>• Possess good communication and interpersonal skill</p>\n<p>• Customer service oriented &amp; positive attitude towards learning</p>\n<p>Location: Biopolis</p>\n<p>Hours of Work: 44 Hours / 5.5 days</p>\n<p>Applicants who are interested in this role are invited to apply with their comprehensive</p>\n<p>resume with full details via \"Apply Now\" button.</p>\n<p>*Only shortlisted applicants will be noticed.</p>",
